title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Deadline Duet Mode for Triple Rewards
content:
Spark explosive breakups in Deadline Duet, the new Adversary Mode that puts the “power up” in “power couple” as you and your partner use twin Shotaro beam trails to destroy opponents in pursuit of Triple Rewards for the next two weeks.

Launch this new mode from the Featured Series and win two matches to satisfy the Weekly Challenge for a sweet GTA$100,000 prize.
